1.Thread Local is a direct child class of Object present in java.langpackage.

2.We use ThreadLocal class to store local Variable of multiple Thread so in lymen terms ThreadLocal is a box which contains LocalVariable for all active Thread.

3.If the Thread has moved into dead state then its corresponding localVariable present in ThreadLocal is eligible for garbage Collection.

4.Thread Local class has following important method.

protected object initialValue();
public Object get();
public void set(T);
public void remove();

5. We can override initialValue method to set initialValue of each Thread LocalVariable.